title: Guess Who’s Making A Comeback In Ye Hai Mohabbatein?
text:
Sukriti Gumber Jan . 6 . 2017 Ye Hai Mohabbatein 
Ye Hai Mohabbatein has been a top TRP garner for Star Plus since the beginning. Currently, the lead protagonists – Raman and Ishita are trying to find the culprit behind Ruhi’s MMS, unaware that the real blackmailer, Suhail, is right in front of them. Anurag Sharma 
Meanwhile, the current parallel track in the show is focussing on Simmi’s love story with Gaurav ( Deepak Wadhwa ). Simmi is ignorant of Gaurav’s evil intentions of trapping her for money. Enter Parmeet! Remember Simmi’s ex husband who was previously a negative character? Parmeet ( Anurag Sharma ) is now a changed man and will try to convince Simmi about Gaurav not being the right choice for her. However, she won’t pay heed to his advice. 
In order to make Simmi see Gaurav’s true colours, Parmeet reportedly takes the disguise of a woman and enters the Bhalla house. Will he be successful in his plan, or will Simmi end up marrying Gaurav? Stay tuned for more updates. 83
